@node "What" "What is Remember Day"


            What is Remember Day?
 
    Remember Day is another program of "Littles Productions" serie
 of Balrog Soft.

    This program remember to you special days: birthdays, cites, etc...

    You can see other programs of "Littles Productions" serie in
 Others productions section.

@{B}--------------------------------------------------------------------------
 @{" <Index> " link "Main"} @{" << Back << " link "English"}
@endnode
@node "Requeriments" "Requeriments"


           Requirements

        Workbench 2.04+, only one...


@{B}--------------------------------------------------------------------------
 @{" <Index> " link "Main"} @{" << Back << " link "English"}
@endnode
@node "How" "How to use"


          How to use

    First... copy RDayPrefs to Prefs directory, and RDayStartup to
 WBStartup.

    Second, run RDayPrefs...

    In RDayPrefs, You see this Gadgets:


        Day: the day that you want remember it...

        Month: the month of the day yo remember...

        After: This options advice X number of days before of the selected
 day.

    Comment: the comment for the advice.

    Add: This option add a comentary...

    Quit: Quit program


    If you want delete a comentary, use ed, and load s:dias... then
 you delete the line of day.


